contents: Move the banana up one space
Move the dollar bill so that it is in the box under the banana
Move the expo eraser up one box
Move the feather to the box below the expo eraser
Move the carrot up one box
Move the pyrex measuring cup down one box
Move the glass cup that is below the chair down one space
Move the water bottle one box over in the same row, so that it is closer to the chair
Move the chair one box over in the same row, so that it will now be next to the water bottle
Move the basketball one box down
Move the round hair brush one box to the side, so that it is next to the ring
Move the headphones one box to the side, in the same direction you just moved the hair brush
Move the red book one box to the side, so that it will not be next to the dog
Move the binoculars one box to the side
Move the tool (wrench?) one box to the side so that it is next to the block with the letter A
Move the block with the letter B one box to the side
Move the coffee mug one box to the side
Move the horseshoe shaped magnet one box down
Move the handcuffs one box down
Move the panda toy one box down
Move the red candle one box down
Move the scissors one box to the side
Move the knife one box down
Move the soap one box to the side, it will be above the knife
move the cassette tape one box down
Move the plane one box to the side, it will then be diagonal from the barrel
Move the sunglasses one box to the side, they will be further away from the saxophone
move the barrel one box down
move the saxophone one box up
move the comb one box up
move the mouse one box up
computer mouse
move the pan one box up
move the piano one box to the side, it will be further away from the pan
